{"tid":1578934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳中國學生在台灣守義大學打港生怎麼辦？","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T15:36:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0813611bb46d1e388b1be8a099c204f6db4a326e","tid":1578934,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"&lt;轉貼ptt&gt;<br />\n中國學生在台灣打港生怎麼辦？<br />\n時間Wed Sep 18 17:29:56 2019<br />\n<br />\n發財市鋼鐵大學有位港生在宿舍的房門佈置連儂牆，貼各種反送中紙條，同校的中國學生看了很刺眼，屢屢上門挑釁，說「在中國人的地方，不承認中國就去死，活著也沒意思」<br />\n，然後口角升級，幾名中國人圍毆港生。事情鬧到學校去，校方將港生叫進小房間面談，要求為了「校譽」息事寧人，別將事情鬧大了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/isu/p/232108673?ref=ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Fisu%2Fp%2F232108673%3Fref%3Dios&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=c7b05856\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/isu/p/232108673?ref=ios</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1568798998.A.835.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1568798998.A.835.html&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=dc73f76f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1568798998.A.835.html</a>"},{"pid":"b8dc78cd4c100f4435dfbd3636f7184edd714b14","tid":1578934,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c07f28778e4fa464d1b41792ebbfd6fbfe95cae","tid":1578934,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事情鬧到學校去，校方將港生叫進小房間面談，要求為了「校譽」息事寧人，別將事情鬧大了</span></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4a413eddf017c5afcabdf8aa6a5153d6f0abcd","tid":1578934,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"pis